title: Logistics bot catcher
descriptionMarkdown:
For when your have (too many spare) logistics bot spread all over your network, you cannot make any more, but you need some for a distant outpost, here's a simple logistics bot 'trap'.

**How to use**

- Put down the blueprint
- Put something that you don't use in your factory, into the provider chest at the bottom the screen. Burner miners are good.
- Get the requester chest to request a large number of what you put in the provider chest
- Don't have so many things in the provider chest so that it is never empty. It must be empty some of the time, so that the bots land
- Watch, as logistics bots land, and fly into the trap

** How it works **
- Bots fly to the provider, then the very short distance to the requester. Then they land in the roboport
- When they land, the purple inserter grabs them from the roboport, if the number of available logistics bots is not zero
- Simples
